## Operating system

STARK works on Linux. 
STARK was tested on CentOS 6.7


## Packages

Python 2.6.6
Make 3.81
ghostscript 8.70


## CPU

STARK does not need a minimum of CPU to work.
Hoever, we recommand at least 2 CPU, ideally 8 CPU.
Note that bigger are your data, more CPU is required.


## RAM

We recommand at least 5Go by CPU (especially for SNPEff annotation and BWA mem alignment).
Thus, STARK works ideally with 32Go of memory




